  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine how safe and effective IMO-8400 is in adults with
      dermatomyositis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety and efficacy of IMO-8400 in adults with active
      dermatomyositis (DM).
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
